    "body": "See: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/35536#issuecomment-4715945494\r\n\r\n`SteadyClockContext` and `FakeNodeClock` are both LimitOne RAII helpers that mock a clock in tests -- the steady clock and the node clock, respectively. Rename the former so the two follow a consistent FakeXClock naming scheme.",
